                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/krd/press/press-releases/2010/11-municipalities-to-try-out-e-voting-in-2011.html?id=591610" title="">
                        11 municipalities to try out e-voting in 2011
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[21.01.2010]</p>
                <p>The government has decided that voters in Bodø, Bremanger, Drammen, Hammerfest, Mandal, Radøy, Re, Tynset, Vefsn, Ålesund and a district in Oslo can take part in an electronic voting trial for the municipal and county council elections in 2011. </p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                                 
