            </a>
            <div class="ArticleImgContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/krd/press/press-releases/2009/ergogroup-to-develop-e-voting-solution.html?id=587734" title="">
                        ErgoGroup to develop e-voting solution
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[04.12.2009]</p>
                <p>ErgoGroup was nominated today as the supplier and developer of a central election administration computer system with a solution for electronic voting. The contract will be signed on 15 December. </p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                                 
