            <div class="ArticleImgContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/krd/press/press-releases/2009/osce-releases-election-observers-report.html?id=587492" title="">
                        OSCE releases election observers’ report
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[30.11.2009]</p>
                <p>The Organization for Security and Co-operation in Europe (OSCE) submitted its report Friday on its observation of the Norwegian parliamentary elections on 14 September. “Input from foreign election observers is important. We need ongoing debate about our democratic system,” says Minister of Local Government and Regional Development Liv Signe Navarsete.</p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                                 
