                    <a href="/en/dep/krd/press/press-releases/2008/the-report-from-the-alesund-committee.html?id=536673" title="">
                        The Report from the Ålesund Committee
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none">Summary</h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[17.11.2008]</p>
                <p>The tragic accident at Fjelltun in Ålesund which cost the lives of five people, and endangered the lives of many more, came as a great shock to us all. It was inconceivable that anything like this could happen in the middle of a town and in a new apartment block. </p>
                
                
